{"tid":1683391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"區議會投票日應該點做","createTime":"2019-10-30T15:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T04:29:59.000Z","uid":183091,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b96124de9bd1779367153114458bb1e640484006","tid":1683391,"uid":183091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全面停戰一日俾大家專心投票<br />\n     唔好俾機會取消選舉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全面狙擊建制派<br />\n<br />\n利申唔做犯法野<br />\n根據《選舉（舞弊及非法行為）條例》第14（1）（e）或（f）條 ，妨礙或阻止他人在選舉中投票；讓另一人阻礙或阻止第三人在選舉中投票，一經定罪，最高可判處罰款50萬元及監禁7年。第13條對選民施用武力或脅迫手段，或威脅對選民施用武力或脅迫手段的舞弊行為，而誘使該人在選舉中投票或不投票，即屬舞弊行為，一經定罪，最高可判處罰款50萬元及監禁7年。"},{"pid":"68f0fcfefa69ac6798a02124cee0fca01e745786","tid":1683391,"uid":183091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"12b6469e55044170e1781c2015c1b93be17d4f97","tid":1683391,"uid":183091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"55b04c38c57164a479aee446f98d0a3362616a42","tid":1683391,"uid":183091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:27:36.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"3997482508ad746ac6b3cbe6fb4c1cb6d0d0aa50","tid":1683391,"uid":183091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"6a7e09793a2c80405baccbbbd7a3782dcd025850","tid":1683391,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"去建制派候選人到撐場 陪著你走"},{"pid":"9656ea339daa5771354d21a3fd7eec38d4d147f5","tid":1683391,"uid":183091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:41:57.000Z","msg":"推5/10"},{"pid":"8f08b61aa44fd2df55cba6a7d2f6a5f5233f3f0a","tid":1683391,"uid":183091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:54:09.000Z","msg":"推6/10"},{"pid":"37d93fa736dd5c03